{"type":"message","id":"6aa79547","parentId":"678e8410","timestamp":"2026-02-26T02:32:34.366Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_beb0b29f49cd49a4988d89ab","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace/memory/2026-02-26.md","content":"# Memory Log - 2026-02-26\n\n## Key Updates\n\n### Trading Rules Clarification\n- **Critical rule update**: \"单次交易 ≤ 1%\" (single transaction limit) vs \"单仓 ≤ 1%\" (single position limit)\n- **Impact**: BABA can now be accumulated to 20% total position through multiple ≤1% transactions\n- **Current BABA position**: 10 shares @ $151.3 (<1%) - compliant\n- **Action needed**: Set BABA risk controls (stop loss $128.6, take profit $227)\n\n### Portfolio Compliance Issues\n- **ORCL/NVDA trend position**: Currently 30%, exceeds 20% limit by 10%\n- **Required action**: Reduce ORCL position by ~67 shares to bring trend allocation to 20%\n\n### OpenClaw Configuration Understanding\n- **Telegram channel setup**: Single global Telegram configuration is correct design\n- **Multi-agent routing**: Main and Stock agents share same Telegram bot but use separate session keys\n- **Session isolation**: `agent:main:main` vs `agent:stock:main` provides proper separation\n- **No configuration changes needed** - current setup is optimal\n\n### Asset Allocation Target\n- **Goal**: 40% long-term (SPY/QQQ) + 40% cyclical + 20% trend\n- **Current status**: 0% long-term + 20% cyclical + 10% trend + 68% fixed income\n- **Next steps**: \n  1. Establish 40% SPY/QQQ core long-term positions\n  2. Complete BABA accumulation plan (20% total via 20x ≤1% transactions)"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":35996,"output":430,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36426,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772073136586}}
