nt version. Please update. Support for old versions may be purchased (at exorbitant rates) by contacting i@izs.me\\nnpm warn deprecated glob@10.5.0: Old versions of glob are not supported, and contain widely publicized security vulnerabilities, which have been fixed in the current version. Please update. Support for old versions may be purchased (at exorbitant rates) by contacting i@izs.me\\nnpm warn deprecated rimraf@3.0.2: Rimraf versions prior to v4 are no longer supported\\nnpm warn deprecated glob@7.2.3: Old versions of glob are not supported, and contain widely publicized security vulnerabilities, which have been fixed in the current version. Please update. Support for old versions may be purchased (at exorbitant rates) by contacting i@izs.me\\nnpm warn deprecated npmlog@5.0.1: This package is no longer supported.\\nnpm warn deprecated gauge@3.0.2: This package is no longer supported.\\nnpm warn deprecated are-we-there-yet@2.0.0: This package is no longer supported.\",\n          \"exitCode\": 0\n        }\n      }\n    ],\n    \"reason\": null,\n    \"durationMs\": 230695\n  }\n}\n\n[Thu 2026-02-26 10:32 GMT+8] 我在telegram上有2个bot，希望 mian_bot与 main通讯， stock_bot与 stock通讯，都是单独私聊？这样的话是不是不能在一个openclaw程序里实现？\n[message_id: 88375d8e-c6f1-4116-98d2-b8ea0c5a4d59]"}],"timestamp":1772073168034}}
{"type":"message","id":"3094084c","parentId":"0f85d357","timestamp":"2026-02-26T02:33:14.618Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"根据您的需求和OpenClaw的架构，我来详细解答这个问题：\n\n## 🎯 **您的需求分析**\n- **main_bot** ↔ **main代理**（单独私聊）\n- **stock_bot** ↔ **stock代理**（单独私聊）\n- 两个独立的Telegram bot，完全分离\n\n## 🔧 **OpenClaw当前限制**\n**单个OpenClaw实例只能配置一个Telegram bot**。这是由OpenClaw的架构决定的：\n- Telegram频道配置在全局`openclaw.json`中\n- `channels.telegram.botToken` 只能设置一个bot token\n- 所有代理共享同一个Telegram频道\n\n## ✅ **可行的解决方案**\n\n### **方案A: 运行两个独立的OpenClaw实例** ⭐（推荐）\n这是最干净、最符合您需求的方案：\n\n**Instance 1 - Main Bot:**\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [{\"id\": \"main\", \"workspace\": \"...\"}]\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"telegram\": {\n      \"botToken\": \"MAIN_BOT_TOKEN\",\n      \"allowFrom\": [\"@worldhello321\"]\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Instance 2 - Stock Bot:**\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [{\"id\": \"stock\", \"workspace\": \"...\"}]\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"telegram\": {\n      \"botToken\": \"STOCK_BOT_TOKEN\", \n      \"allowFrom\": [\"@worldhello321\"]\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**优点：**\n- 完全隔离，无任何干扰\n- 每个bot只处理对应的代理\n- 配置简单清晰\n- 符合您的\"单独私聊\"需求\n\n**部署方式：**\n- 使用不同的配置文件路径\n- 使用不同的端口（gateway.port）\n- 可以在同一台机器上运行\n\n### **方案B: 单一bot + 消息路由**（当前状态）\n继续使用当前配置，通过消息内容或命令前缀来区分：\n\n- `/main [message]` → 路由到main代理  \n- `/stock [message]` → 路由到stock代理\n\n**缺点：**\n- 不是真正的\"单独私聊\"\n- 需要用户记住命令前缀\n- 与您的需求不完全匹配\n\n### **方案C: 等待OpenClaw多频道支持**\nOpenClaw未来可能会支持多Telegram bot配置，但目前没有这个功能。\n\n## 📋 **实施建议**\n\n**强烈推荐方案A**（两个独立实例），因为：\n1. **完全满足您的需求** - 真正的单独私聊\n2. **架构清晰** - 无耦合，易于维护  \n3. **安全隔离** - 一个实例的问题不会影响另一个\n4. **资源消耗低** - OpenClaw实例很轻量\n\n**具体步骤：**\n1. 创建第二个OpenClaw配置目录\n2. 复制并修改配置文件，只保留对应代理和bot token\n3. 使用不同端口启动第二个实例\n4. 在系统服务中分别管理两个实例\n\n这样您就可以实现：\n- **@main_bot** → 只与main代理对话\n- **@stock_bot** → 只与stock代理对话\n\n完全符合您的\"单独私聊\"要求！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":38003,"output":724,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38727,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772073168035}}
