{"type":"message","id":"e36caa69","parentId":"fb20bd41","timestamp":"2026-02-26T03:02:36.312Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent - 协调确认\n\n完美！Stock Agent状态良好，所有关键任务都已明确：\n\n**立即待办事项：**\n1. **BABA风控设置** - 止损$128.6，止盈$227\n2. **ORCL/NVDA减仓** - 降低10%趋势仓位至合规水平\n\n**后续计划：**\n3. **BABA分批加仓** - 通过20次≤1%交易达到20%目标\n4. **SPY/QQQ建仓** - 建立40%长线核心仓位\n\n需要我协助协调任何具体操作吗？比如生成详细的交易指令模板，或者帮您执行具体的下单步骤？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":40351,"output":160,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40511,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772074946644}}
