{"type":"message","id":"8c443b6d","parentId":"bc48cb4c","timestamp":"2026-02-26T04:49:51.608Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0939f5c4b9ba47c8819eb26d","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"15b6e921-93ea-4620-9589-4b3dfc901f1d\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"name\": \"hourly-heartbeat\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1771904760464,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1772078441863,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"0 8-21 * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"main\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"systemEvent\",\n        \"text\": \"⏰ Heartbeat checkpoint. 读取 HEARTBEAT.md 并执行检查。如果无待办事项，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1772082000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1772078400008,\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 41855,\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"29dc61f3-373f-442a-bc14-f5d5fc61b7d3\",\n      \"name\": \"workspace-backup\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1770696979999,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1772028038116,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 22 * * *\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"main\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"systemEvent\",\n        \"text\": \"执行每日备份\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1772114400000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1772028000010,\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 38106,\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"7fd6e0a7-19f8-4d6d-bb27-4d85bbcbb74f\",\n      \"name\": \"memory-archive\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1770696986910,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1770696986910,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 3 1 * *\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"main\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"systemEvent\",\n        \"text\": \"执行月度归档\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1772305200000\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"jobs":[{"id":"15b6e921-93ea-4620-9589-4b3dfc901f1d","agentId":"main","name":"hourly-heartbeat","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1771904760464,"updatedAtMs":1772078441863,"schedule":{"expr":"0 8-21 * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"main","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"systemEvent","text":"⏰ Heartbeat checkpoint. 读取 HEARTBEAT.md 并执行检查。如果无待办事项，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1772082000000,"lastRunAtMs":1772078400008,"lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":41855,"consecutiveErrors":0}},{"id":"29dc61f3-373f-442a-bc14-f5d5fc61b7d3","name":"workspace-backup","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1770696979999,"updatedAtMs":1772028038116,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 22 * * *"},"sessionTarget":"main","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"systemEvent","text":"执行每日备份"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1772114400000,"lastRunAtMs":1772028000010,"lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":38106,"consecutiveErrors":0}},{"id":"7fd6e0a7-19f8-4d6d-bb27-4d85bbcbb74f","name":"memory-archive","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1770696986910,"updatedAtMs":1770696986910,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 3 1 * *"},"sessionTarget":"main","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"systemEvent","text":"执行月度归档"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1772305200000}}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772081391605}}
{"type":"message","id":"1bc39452","parentId":"8c443b6d","timestamp":"2026-02-26T04:50:04.556Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent - 定时任务检查结果\n\n✅ **定时任务配置正常！** 我找到了3个已配置的定时任务：\n\n### **当前定时任务列表：**\n\n1. **hourly-heartbeat** ⏰\n   - **时间**: 每天8-21点每小时执行（`0 8-21 * * *`）\n   - **功能**: 执行心跳检查，读取HEARTBEAT.md\n   - **状态**: 正常运行（最近一次执行：12:00）\n\n2. **workspace-backup** 💾  \n   - **时间**: 每天22:00执行（`0 22 * * *`）\n   - **功能**: 执行每日备份\n   - **状态**: 正常运行（最近一次执行：今天22:00）\n\n3. **memory-archive** 📁\n   - **时间**: 每月1日3:00执行（`0 3 1 * *`）\n   - **功能**: 执行月度归档  \n   - **状态**: 已配置，等待下次执行\n\n### **心跳任务工作正常**\n您看到的\"Read HEARTBEAT.md...\"消息正是**hourly-heartbeat**定时任务在正常工作！这个任务每小时（8-21点）自动触发，确保系统健康检查。\n\n所以您的定时任务设置是完全正确的，系统正在按预期执行。有什么特定的定时任务您想调整或添加吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":63472,"output":328,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63800,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772081391608}}
