{"type":"message","id":"f86a11a6","parentId":"41d2c779","timestamp":"2026-02-26T04:56:04.926Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d2a88e877c2b49bc94b5953c","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"mem0 ai memory platform features architecture\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 1884,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGitHub - mem0ai/mem0: Universal memory layer for AI Agents\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/mem0ai/mem0\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIt <strong>remembers user preferences, adapts to individual needs, and continuously learns over time</strong>—ideal for customer support chatbots, AI assistants, and autonomous systems. ... Get up and running in minutes with automatic updates, analytics, and ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nMem0 - The Memory Layer for your AI Apps\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://mem0.ai/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>Track TTL, size, and access for every memory—debug, optimise, and audit with ease</strong>. The user weighs 72 kg, targets 130 g protein daily, and wants 20 pull-ups. ... Mem0 is SOC 2 &amp; HIPAA compliant with BYOK making your data stays secure and ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"mem0.ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOverview - Mem0\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://docs.mem0.ai/platform/overview\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGraph memory, async clients, and rerankers. Metadata filters and per-request toggles. LangChain, CrewAI, Vercel AI SDK. Track activity and manage workspaces. Evaluating self-hosting instead? Jump to the Platform vs OSS comparison to see trade-offs before you commit.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"docs.mem0.ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n[2504.19413] Mem0: Building Production-Ready AI Agents with Scalable Long-Term Memory\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://arxiv.org/abs/2504.19413\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWe introduce Mem0, a scalable memory-centric architecture that addresses this issue by <strong>dynamically extracting, consolidating, and retrieving salient information from ongoing conversations</strong>.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"April 28, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"arxiv.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nMem0: The Memory layer for your AI apps | Y Combinator\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ycombinator.com/companies/mem0\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThat’s where Mem0’s hybrid ... as it learns. ... Mem0 employs a <strong>hybrid datastore architecture that combines graph, vector, and key-value stores to store and manage memories effectively</strong>....\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.ycombinator.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"mem0 ai memory platform features architecture","provider":"brave","count":5,"tookMs":1884,"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGitHub - mem0ai/mem0: Universal memory layer for AI Agents\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTE