{"type":"message","id":"c4af0c5e","parentId":"f81734b8","timestamp":"2026-02-26T05:54:21.474Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent - Mem0集成实施\n\n我将为您实施Mem0直接安装方案。让我逐步创建所有必要的文件和配置。\n\n### **Step 1: 创建Mem0目录结构**\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e185e2560bdc456293acf754","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/README.md","content":"# Mem0 Local Installation\n\nMem0 OSS (Open Source) installation for OpenClaw multi-agent system.\n\n## Directory Structure\n- `data/` - Persistent data storage (backup this directory)\n- `config/` - Configuration files\n- `logs/` - Runtime logs\n- `init_mem0.py` - Initialization script\n\n## Migration\nTo migrate to a new machine:\n1. Copy the entire `mem0/` directory\n2. Install mem0ai: `pip install mem0ai`\n3. Set OPENAI_API_KEY environment variable\n4. Run initialization script\n\nAll memory data is stored in the `data/` directory and will be preserved across migrations."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":83589,"output":223,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83812,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772084949708}}
