{"type":"message","id":"46adb6ac","parentId":"627df42e","timestamp":"2026-02-26T05:57:15.549Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I see that you're using the Qwen model from Alibaba Cloud (bailian) rather than OpenAI. Mem0 by default uses OpenAI, but it can be configured to use other models. Let me create a configuration that works with your existing setup.\n\n### **Step 9: Update Mem0 Configuration for Qwen**\n\nLet me create a custom configuration that uses your existing Qwen model:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9c34ab0da845483cb01381ae","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/config/mem0_config_qwen.yaml","content":"# Mem0 configuration for Qwen model (Alibaba Cloud)\nvector_store:\n  provider: \"qdrant\"\n  config:\n    path: \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/data/qdrant\"\n    collection_name: \"mem0_memories\"\n\nhistory_db:\n  path: \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/data/sqlite/history.db\"\n\nllm:\n  provider: \"openai\"  # Qwen is OpenAI-compatible\n  config:\n    model: \"qwen3-max-2026-01-23\"\n    base_url: \"https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/v1\"\n    api_key: \"${OPENCLAW_QWEN_API_KEY}\"\n\nembedder:\n  provider: \"openai\"  # Using OpenAI embeddings for now\n  config:\n    model: \"text-embedding-3-small\"\n    api_key: \"${OPENAI_API_KEY}\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":89836,"output":323,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90159,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772085422201}}
