{"type":"message","id":"67aaf781","parentId":"ce85003f","timestamp":"2026-02-26T05:58:19.835Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### **Step 11: Create Environment Setup Script**\n\nLet me create a script to set up the environment properly:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2ed2e99f6c4d41a69f80ca23","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/setup_env.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n\n# Mem0 Environment Setup Script\n# This script sets up the environment for Mem0 with Qwen\n\necho \"Setting up Mem0 environment...\"\n\n# Create data directories\nmkdir -p /Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/data/qdrant\nmkdir -p /Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/data/sqlite\nmkdir -p /Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/config\n\necho \"Data directories created.\"\n\n# Set up Python path\nexport PYTHONPATH=\"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0:$PYTHONPATH\"\n\n# Note: Qwen API key is already configured in OpenClaw\n# No need to set OPENAI_API_KEY\n\necho \"Environment setup complete!\"\necho \"\"\necho \"To use Mem0 with your agents:\"\necho \"1. Import the custom client: from custom_mem0_client import QwenMem0Client\"\necho \"2. Initialize: mem0_client = QwenMem0Client()\"\necho \"3. Use add_memory() and search_memory() methods\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":90085,"output":279,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90364,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772085489314}}
