Cloud</strong>. Qwen models can understand and analyze natural language and multimodal data, such as image and video. They provide services...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.alibabacloud.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nQwen - Wikipedia\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Qwen\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>Alibaba launched a beta of Qwen in April 2023 under the name Tongyi Qianwen, then opened it for public use in September 2023 after regulatory clearance</strong>. The model&#x27;s architecture was based on the Llama architecture developed by Meta AI.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"3 days ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"en.wikipedia.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGitHub - QwenLM/Qwen3.5: Qwen3.5 is the large language model series developed by Qwen team, Alibaba Cloud.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen3.5\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>Alibaba Cloud Model Studio provides first-class support for Qwen3.5</strong>, which is compatible with various API specifications, including OpenAI and Anthropic, making it simple for you to try Qwen3.5 in your own applications.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"mem0 ai supported LLMs qwen alibaba","provider":"brave","count":5,"tookMs":1071,"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n🤖AI Agents Weekly: Qwen3, mem0, Llama API, Bamba, Qwen2.5-Omni-3B\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://nlp.elvissaravia.com/p/ai-agents-weekly-qwen3-mem0-ll