AL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://github.com/QwenLM","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAlibaba Cloud&#x27;s general-purpose AI models. Qwen has 40 repositories available. <strong>Follow their code on GitHub</strong>.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"github.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGitHub - QwenLM/Qwen: The official repo of Qwen (通义千问) chat & pretrained large language model proposed by Alibaba Cloud.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDashScope is the large language model API service provided by Alibaba Cloud, which now supports Qwen. Note that the models behind DashScope are in-house versions temporarily without details provided. The services include qwen-turbo and qwen-plus, where the former one runs faster and the latter achieves better performance.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"github.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGitHub - QwenLM/Qwen3.5: Qwen3.5 is the large language model series developed by Qwen team, Alibaba Cloud.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen3.5","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n<strong>Alibaba Cloud Model Studio provides first-class support for Qwen3.5</strong>, which is compatible with various API specifications, including OpenAI and Anthropic, making it simple for you to try Qwen3.5 in your own applications.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"github.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGitHub - QwenLM/qwen-code: An open-source AI agent that lives in your terminal.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://github.com/QwenLM/qwen-code","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nOpenAI-compatible: <strong>Alibaba Cloud Bailian, ModelScope, OpenAI, OpenRouter, and other OpenAI-compatible providers</strong> ... The recommended way to configure models and providers is by editing ~/.qwen/settings.json (create it if it doesn&#x27;t exist).\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"github.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGitHub - QwenLM/Qwen3: Qwen3 is the large language model series developed by Qwen team, Alibaba Cloud.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen3","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nQwen3 is supported by multiple inference frameworks. Here we demonstrate the usage of SGLang, vLLM and TensorRT-LLM. You can also find Qwen3 models from various inference providers, e.g., Alibaba Cloud Model Studio.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"github.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772086580965}}
{"type":"message","id":"bc25607e","parentId":"f820b1b2","timestamp":"2026-02-26T06:16:53.121Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent - Mem0架构真相澄清\n\n您说得完全正确！让我重新分析Mem0的真实架构：\n\n### **🔍 Mem0真实架构分析**\n\n**Mem0确实是一个本地向量库，但需要LLM进行智能处理：**\n\n1. **向量存储**: ✅ 完全本地（Qdrant/Chroma）\n2. **记忆提取**: ❌ 需要LLM（从对话中提取关键信息）\n3. **记忆更新**: ❌ 需要LLM（合并和优化记忆）\n4. **语义搜索**: ✅ 本地向量相似度计算\n\n### **🎯 核心问题**\n\nMem0的**智能性**来自于LLM，而**存储**是本地的。具体来说：\n\n- **存储层**: 100%本地（您的数据安全）\n- **处理层**: 需要LLM API（用于理解对话内容）\n\n### **💡 解决方案**\n\n既然您使用的是**Qwen模型**，而Qwen支持**OpenAI兼容API**，我们可以这样配置：\n\n**Qwen OpenAI兼容模式：**\n```python\nconfig = {\n    \"llm\": {\n        \"provider\": \"openai\",\n        \"config\": {\n            \"model\": \"qwen3-max-2026-01-23\",\n            \"api_key\": \"your-qwen-api-key\", \n            \"base_url\": \"https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/v1\"\n        }\n    },\n    \"embedder\": {\n        \"provider\": \"openai\", \n        \"config\": {\n            \"model\": \"text-embedding-3-small\",\n            \"api_key\": \"your-qwen-api-key\",\n            \"base_url\": \"https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/v1\"\n        }\n    },\n    \"vector_store\": {\n        \"provider\": \"qdrant\",\n        \"config\": {\n            \"path\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/data/qdrant\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### **✅ 验证您的Qwen配置**\n\n从您的OpenClaw配置中，我看到：\n- **Base URL**: `https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/v1`\n- **Model**: `qwen3-max-2026-01-23`\n- **API Key**: 已配置\n\n这完全符合OpenAI兼容格式！\n\n### **🔧 修正后的集成方案**\n\n让我创建正确的配置：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_28ee2467d6744317815dac4b","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/config/mem0_qwen_config.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nMem0 configuration for Qwen model (OpenAI compatible)\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nfrom mem0 import Memory\n\ndef create_qwen_mem0():\n    \"\"\"Create Mem0 instance configured for Qwen model\"\"\"\n    \n    # Get Qwen API key from environment or OpenClaw config\n    qwen_api_key = os.getenv(\"QWEN_API_KEY\", \"your-qwen-api-key-here\")\n    \n    config = {\n        \"llm\": {\n            \"provider\": \"openai\",\n            \"config\": {\n                \"model\": \"qwen3-max-2026-01-23\",\n                \"api_key\": qwen_api_key,\n                \"base_url\": \"https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/v1\",\n                \"temperature\": 0.0\n            }\n        },\n        \"embedder\": {\n            \"provider\": \"openai\",\n            \"config\": {\n                \"model\": \"text-embedding-3-small\",  # Qwen may not support this, may need to use their embedding model\n                \"api_key\": qwen_api_key,\n                \"base_url\": \"https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/v1\"\n            }\n        },\n        \"vector_store\": {\n            \"provider\": \"qdrant\",\n            \"config\": {\n                \"path\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/data/qdrant\",\n                \"collection_name\": \"mem0_memories\"\n            }\n        },\n        \"history_db_path\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/data/sqlite/history.db\"\n    }\n    \n    return Memory.from_config(config)\n\n# Test the configuration\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    try:\n        memory = create_qwen_mem0()\n        print(\"✅ Qwen Mem0 configuration created successfully!\")\n        print(f\"Data path: /Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/data/\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ Configuration error: {e}\")"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":103835,"output":997,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104832,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772086580974}}
