{"type":"message","id":"dfed6e6a","parentId":"16e4a656","timestamp":"2026-02-26T06:26:02.029Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent - API密钥配置指南\n\n### **🔑 您需要提供Qwen API密钥**\n\n从您的OpenClaw配置中，我看到您使用的是阿里云的Qwen模型：\n- **Base URL**: `https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/v1`\n- **Model**: `qwen3-max-2026-01-23`\n\n### **🔧 配置方法**\n\n**方法1: 环境变量（推荐）**\n```bash\n# 在终端中设置\nexport OPENAI_API_KEY=\"your-qwen-api-key\"\nexport OPENAI_BASE_URL=\"https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/v1\"\n\n# 然后运行Mem0\npython /Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/demo_final.py\n```\n\n**方法2: 修改配置文件**\n让我为您创建一个包含API密钥的配置文件：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ca6336853cd04f78ac922e67","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/config/api_config.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nAPI Configuration for Mem0 with Qwen\n\"\"\"\n\n# 替换下面的 \"your-qwen-api-key\" 为您的实际API密钥\nQWEN_API_KEY = \"your-qwen-api-key\"\n\n# Qwen API配置\nMEM0_CONFIG = {\n    \"llm\": {\n        \"provider\": \"openai\",\n        \"config\": {\n            \"model\": \"qwen3-max-2026-01-23\",\n            \"api_key\": QWEN_API_KEY,\n            \"base_url\": \"https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/v1\",\n            \"temperature\": 0.0\n        }\n    },\n    \"embedder\": {\n        \"provider\": \"openai\",\n        \"config\": {\n            \"model\": \"text-embedding-3-small\",\n            \"api_key\": QWEN_API_KEY,\n            \"base_url\": \"https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/v1\"\n        }\n    },\n    \"vector_store\": {\n        \"provider\": \"qdrant\",\n        \"config\": {\n            \"path\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/data/qdrant\",\n            \"collection_name\": \"mem0_memories\"\n        }\n    },\n    \"history_db_path\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/data/sqlite/history.db\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":126401,"output":529,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens