{"type":"message","id":"7e037575","parentId":"1e8ac1bf","timestamp":"2026-02-26T06:26:12.716Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**方法3: 直接在代码中设置**\n```python\n# 在您的代理代码中添加\nimport os\nos.environ[\"OPENAI_API_KEY\"] = \"your-qwen-api-key\"\nos.environ[\"OPENAI_BASE_URL\"] = \"https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/v1\"\n```\n\n### **📋 需要您提供的信息**\n\n请提供您的 **Qwen API密钥**，格式类似于：\n- `sk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx`\n- 或者阿里云DashScope的API密钥\n\n### **🔐 安全建议**\n\n1. **不要在代码中硬编码** - 使用环境变量或配置文件\n2. **配置文件权限** - 设置为仅您可读：`chmod 600 api_config.py`\n3. **备份排除** - 确保API密钥不被Git提交\n\n### **⚙️ 自动配置脚本**\n\n如果您提供API密钥，我可以帮您：\n\n1. **自动配置环境变量**\n2. **创建安全的配置文件**  \n3. **测试Mem0连接**\n4. **集成到各代理中**\n\n**请提供您的Qwen API密钥，我将立即完成配置！**\n\n或者，如果您希望我指导您手动配置，请告诉我您的API密钥，我会给出具体的配置步骤。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":126635,"output":278,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126913,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772087162061}}
