{"type":"message","id":"37f02134","parentId":"60405949","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:02:12.783Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"从搜索结果中，我看到Mem0确实支持自定义模型名！在OpenAI配置示例中：\n\n```python\nconfig = {\n \"llm\": {\n \"provider\": \"openai\",\n \"config\": {\n \"model\": \"gpt-4.1-nano-2025-04-14\",\n \"temperature\": 0.2,\n \"max_tokens\": 2000,\n }\n }\n}\n```\n\n所以我的配置应该是正确的。让我检查为什么模型名没有被正确使用。\n\n可能问题出在Mem0的内部实现。让我尝试一个更简单的配置：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_524d83dcb1a342fb93fac01b","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/simple_test.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nimport os\nfrom mem0 import Memory\n\n# Set environment variables\nos.environ[\"OPENAI_API_KEY\"] = \"sk-sp-1f07658367b9409393e075f9f63490bf\"\nos.environ[\"OPENAI_BASE_URL\"] = \"https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/v1\"\n\n# Simple config with custom model\nconfig = {\n    \"llm\": {\n        \"provider\": \"openai\",\n        \"config\": {\n            \"model\": \"qwen3-max-2026-01-23\",\n            \"temperature\": 0.0\n        }\n    },\n    \"vector_store\": {\n        \"provider\": \"qdrant\",\n        \"config\": {\n            \"path\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/mem0/data/qdrant\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n\nprint(\"Creating Mem0 instance...\")\ntry:\n    memory = Memory.from_config(config)\n    print(\"✅ Mem0 initialized successfully!\")\n    \n    # Test adding memory\n    messages = [\n        {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Hello, I'm testing Mem0 with Qwen!\"},\n        {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Great! I'll remember this test.\"}\n    ]\n    \n    print(\"🔄 Adding test memory...\")\n    memory.add(messages, user_id=\"test_user\")\n    print(\"✅ Test memory added successfully!\")\n    \n    # Test searching\n    print(\"🔍 Searching for memories...\")\n    results = memory.search(\"test\", user_id=\"test_user\")\n    print(f\"✅ Found {len(results['results'])} memories!\")\n    \nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"❌ Error: {e}\")"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":144460,"output":534,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144994,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772089313123}}
