{"type":"message","id":"8daa3155","parentId":"418aa5ff","timestamp":"2026-02-26T08:09:59.766Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent - Agent日志写入机制说明\n\n让我检查当前的日志写入机制：\n\n### **🔍 当前日志写入情况**\n\n**1. Daily Memory Logs (每日记忆日志)**\n- ✅ **Main Agent**: 自动写入 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- ✅ **Stock Agent**: 有独立的daily log系统  \n- ✅ **MCS Agent**: 有独立的daily log系统\n- **触发时机**: 手动触发或重要事件时\n\n**2. Heartbeat检查**\n- ✅ **当前配置**: 每小时执行heartbeat检查（8-21点）\n- ❌ **但不自动写入日志**: heartbeat只做健康检查，不自动生成日志\n\n**3. Session Transcripts (会话记录)**\n- ✅ **自动记录**: 所有代理的对话都自动保存在 `sessions/*.jsonl`\n- **位置**: \n  - Main: `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/`\n  - Stock: `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/sessions/`\n  - MCS: `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/mcs/sessions/`\n\n### **📋 当前Heartbeat任务配置**\n\n```yaml\nhourly-heartbeat:\n  schedule: \"0 8-21 * * *\"  # 8-21点每小时\n  payload: \"⏰ Heartbeat checkpoint. 读取 HEARTBEAT.md 并执行检查。如果无待办事项，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。\"\n```\n\n**当前heartbeat只做检查，不写入日志**。\n\n### **💡 建议的增强方案**\n\n**选项A: Heartbeat自动日志写入**\n- 修改heartbeat任务，在检查后自动写入当日摘要\n- 包含各代理的重要状态和行动项\n\n**选项B: 保持现状 + 手动触发**\n- 继续手动在需要时写入日志\n- heartbeat保持轻量级健康检查\n\n**选项C: 混合模式**\n- Heartbeat只在有重要事件时写入日志\n- 平时只做健康检查\n\n### **📊 当前实际日志文件**\n\n让我检查现有的日志文件：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d9dcbe5ca6c54a128c32ffc2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace/memory/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":156164,"output":525,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":156689,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772093377514}}
