{"type":"message","id":"06e13101","parentId":"a3ed391c","timestamp":"2026-02-26T08:11:02.322Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看到Main Agent的daily log已经存在（`2026-02-26.md`），并且有一个指向shared/memory的符号链接。\n\n### **✅ 当前状态总结**\n\n- **Daily Logs**: ✅ 各代理有独立日志系统\n- **Session Transcripts**: ✅ 自动记录所有对话  \n- **Heartbeat**: ❌ 不自动写入日志（只做健康检查）\n- **Shared Memory**: ✅ 通过脚本手动写入重要跨代理信息\n\n您希望我将heartbeat任务修改为自动写入日志吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":156837,"output":124,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":156961,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772093399800}}
