{"type":"message","id":"1328da70","parentId":"d33e07c3","timestamp":"2026-02-26T08:35:21.141Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### **✅ Heartbeat增强版实施完成！**\n\n## **📊 三个Agent独立Heartbeat任务已创建**\n\n### **🎯 Main Agent Heartbeat**\n- **时间**: 每小时8-21点\n- **内容**: 系统协调状态、代理通信协议、整体健康状况\n- **文件**: `agents/main/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n\n### **📈 Stock Agent Heartbeat**  \n- **时间**: 每小时8-21点\n- **内容**: 投资组合状态、持仓摘要、交易合规性\n- **文件**: `agents/stock/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n\n### **🎓 MCS Agent Heartbeat**\n- **时间**: 每小时8-21点  \n- **内容**: 职业发展进展、学习计划状态、技术能力评估\n- **文件**: `agents/mcs/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n\n### **🔄 工作流程**\n1. **每小时自动触发** (8-21点)\n2. **各Agent生成当日状态摘要**\n3. **写入各自的daily log文件**\n4. **保持专业化和独立性**\n5. **每日22:00自动备份所有日志**\n\n现在您的三个Agent都具备了自动记忆更新能力！每个Agent都会在自己的专业领域内定期记录重要状态和进展。\n\n需要我演示一下heartbeat任务的执行效果吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":161332,"output":294,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":161626,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772094904136}}
