{"type":"message","id":"0fda6b7c","parentId":"1923921a","timestamp":"2026-02-26T09:05:59.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**限制**: Main Agent的cron任务只能使用`systemEvent` payload类型。\n\n### **💡 替代解决方案**\n\n**方案A: 修改systemEvent处理逻辑**\n- 在systemEvent中检测heartbeat消息\n- 自动执行日志写入 + sync-to-sqlite.sh\n\n**方案B: 保持现状 + 手动同步**\n- 继续手动执行sync-to-sqlite.sh\n- heartbeat专注于状态检查\n\n**方案C: 创建独立的sync任务**\n- 每30分钟自动执行sync-to-sqlite.sh\n- 与heartbeat任务分离\n\n### **📋 当前最佳实践**\n\n鉴于当前限制，我建议：\n\n1. **继续使用当前heartbeat**（专注于状态检查）\n2. **在需要时手动执行sync**：\n   ```bash\n   cd /Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace\n   ./memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh\n   ```\n3. **每日备份时自动包含最新日志**（即使未同步到SQLite）\n\n这样既保持了heartbeat的轻量级，又确保了数据的完整性。\n\n您希望我实施哪种方案？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":178129,"output":240,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":178369,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772096748766}}
