{"type":"message","id":"4e00ad6e","parentId":"12ddaa03","timestamp":"2026-02-26T09:12:48.362Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-02-26 17:12 GMT+8] 我现在怎么感觉 heatbeat过于频繁了，你检查下 现在3个agent，有3个调度任务，分别heatbeat，如果以后有多个agent，比如10个，调度任务太多了，建议合并成1个heatbeat调度任务，让main进行heatbeat，然后让main进行自己的健康检查，然后记录自己的memory， 然后分别与其他agent交互完成检查和memory记录\n[message_id: 8cb091c9-ff5f-46be-9ae9-8ead1f0502ff]"}],"timestamp":1772097168356}}
{"type":"message","id":"e274afa2","parentId":"4e00ad6e","timestamp":"2026-02-26T09:13:30.113Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent - Heartbeat任务优化建议\n\n您提出的建议非常合理！**当前的3个独立heartbeat任务确实存在冗余和扩展性问题**。\n\n### **🔍 当前问题分析**\n\n**现有架构问题**:\n- ❌ **任务冗余**: 3个独立的cron任务，每小时各执行1次 = 每小时3次系统调用\n- ❌ **扩展性差**: 10个agent = 10个heartbeat任务，管理复杂度指数级增长\n- ❌ **资源浪费**: 多个任务重复执行系统检查\n- ❌ **协调困难**: 各agent独立执行，缺乏统一协调\n\n### **✅ 优化方案：单点协调模式**\n\n**新架构设计**:\n```\nSingle Heartbeat Task (Main Agent)\n│\n├── Main Agent Health Check → memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n├── Stock Agent Coordination → Stock Agent → memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md  \n├── MCS Agent Coordination → MCS Agent → memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n└── Future Agent Coordination → [Agent] → memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n```\n\n### **⚙️ 实施步骤**\n\n#### **Step 1: 删除现有heartbeat任务**\n- `stock-heartbeat` ❌\n- `mcs-heartbeat` ❌  \n- 保留 `hourly-heartbeat` (重命名为 `main-coordinator-heartbeat`) ✅\n\n#### **Step 2: 增强Main Agent heartbeat逻辑**\n```python\n# Main Agent Heartbeat Enhanced Logic\ndef main_heartbeat():\n    # 1. Main Agent自身健康检查\n    main_health_check()\n    write_to_main_memory()\n    \n    # 2. 协调Stock Agent\n    stock_status = send_message_to_stock(\"执行heartbeat检查\")\n    write_stock_status_to_main_memory(stock_status)\n    \n    # 3. 协调MCS Agent  \n    mcs_status = send_message_to_mcs(\"执行heartbeat检查\")\n    write_mcs_status_to_main_memory(mcs_status)\n    \n    # 4. 自动同步所有memory到SQLite\n    sync_all_memories_to_index()\n```\n\n#### **Step 3: 各Agent提供heartbeat接口**\n- **Stock Agent**: 提供`/heartbeat`端点，返回投资状态摘要\n- **MCS Agent**: 提供`/heartbeat`端点，返回职业发展摘要\n- **Future Agents**: 统一heartbeat接口标准\n\n### **🎯 优化后优势**\n\n| 方面 | 当前架构 | 优化后架构 |\n|------|----------|------------|\n| **任务数量** | N个heartbeat任务 | 1个heartbeat任务 |\n| **系统调用** | 每小时N次 | 每小时1次 |\n| **扩展性** | 线性增长 | 恒定不变 |\n| **协调性** | 独立执行 | 统一协调 |\n| **资源消耗** | 高 | 低 |\n| **维护复杂度** | 高 | 低 |\n\n### **📋 执行计划**\n\n**立即行动**:\n1. **删除** `stock-heartbeat` 和 `mcs-heartbeat` 任务\n2. **更新** `hourly-heartbeat` 任务为协调模式\n3. **修改** Main Agent的heartbeat处理逻辑\n\n**后续优化**:\n4. **标准化** 各Agent的heartbeat接口\n5. **自动化** memory同步到SQLite\n6. **监控** 单点协调的性能和可靠性\n\n### **🔧 技术实现细节**\n\n**Main Agent heartbeat payload**:\n```json\n{\n  \"kind\": \"systemEvent\",\n  \"text\": \"⏰ Coordinator Heartbeat. Execute health checks for all agents and update memory logs.\"\n}\n```\n\n**各Agent响应格式**:\n```json\n{\n  \"agent_id\": \"stock\",\n  \"status\": \"healthy\",\n  \"summary\": \"投资组合状态摘要...\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-02-26T17:15:00\"\n}\n```\n\n这个优化方案将显著提升系统的可扩展性和维护性。需要我立即实施这个优化吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":181579,"output":880,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":182459,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772097168360}}
