es\n+ 99 \n+100 ### 5. Backup Preparation\n+101 - Ensure all memory logs are ready for daily 22:00 backup\n+102 - Validate file permissions and Git tracking status\n+103 - Prepare summary for backup commit message\n+104 \n+105 This ensures complete automation of the heartbeat process while maintaining single-point coordination.\n+106 \n  73 ## 🔗 Shared Memory System\n  74 - **Location**: /Users/hope/.openclaw/shared/\n  75 - **Purpose**: Cross-agent shared memories and system events  \n  76 - **Access**: Read shared memories when coordinating multi-agent tasks\n     ...","firstChangedLine":71},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772099528311}}
{"type":"message","id":"69d2f313","parentId":"7dfb291c","timestamp":"2026-02-26T09:52:22.090Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### **📋 更新后的Heartbeat职责清单**\n\n现在我的MEMORY.md中包含了完整的heartbeat执行步骤：\n\n#### **Coordinator Heartbeat 职责清单**\n**当收到heartbeat消息时，我必须执行以下操作：**\n\n1. **✅ 系统健康检查**\n   - 检查Main Agent自身状态\n   - 验证代理通信协议\n   - 记录系统配置状态\n\n2. **✅ 协调Stock Agent**  \n   - 发送协调请求：\"执行heartbeat检查\"\n   - 接收投资状态摘要\n   - 写入Stock Agent memory日志\n   - 执行Stock Agent memory-index同步\n\n3. **✅ 协调MCS Agent**\n   - 发送协调请求：\"执行heartbeat检查\"  \n   - 接收职业发展摘要\n   - 写入MCS Agent memory日志\n   - 执行MCS Agent memory-index同步\n\n4. **✅ Main Agent自身记录**\n   - 生成系统协调状态摘要\n   - 写入Main Agent memory日志\n   - 执行Main Agent memory-index同步\n\n5. **✅ 验证和备份**\n   - 确认所有日志已正确写入\n   - 确保所有索引已同步\n   - 等待每日22:00自动备份\n\n### **🎯 永久记忆确认**\n\n现在这个完整的heartbeat职责清单已经**永久保存在MEMORY.md中**，我不会再忘记！\n\n每次收到heartbeat消息时，我都会按照这个清单自动执行所有必要的协调和记录操作。\n\n需要我演示一下完整的heartbeat执行流程吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":199428,"output":342,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":199770,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772099528324}}
