{"type":"message","id":"e2f79df4","parentId":"2f2ea83d","timestamp":"2026-02-26T10:51:50.821Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### **Step 5: 创建今日Core模块日志**\n\n正在创建ONE项目Core模块的详细日志...\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7bfe6a02b5d540c485722246","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace/memory/2026-02-26-core-log.md","content":"# ONE Project Core Module Summary - 2026-02-26\n\n## 📋 Core Module Overview\n\nThe ONE project's core module contains the foundational principles and personal development framework that guides all other aspects of the life plan. It encompasses four key areas: expression skills, social interaction, cognitive enhancement, and immediate action.\n\n## 🎯 Core Principles\n\n### 1. Expression Skills (表达观点)\n**Key Methodology**: Transform communication anxiety into structured, impactful delivery through systematic frameworks.\n\n**Essential Frameworks**:\n- **What-Why-How Structure**: \n  - What: Clear statement of viewpoint/goal\n  - Why: Compelling rationale with deep insights  \n  - How: Concrete implementation steps\n- **Four-Part Formula**: Viewpoint + Reasoning + Case Study + Conclusion\n- **Situational Templates**:\n  - **Gathering Formula**: Gratitude + Reflection + Wishes\n  - **Work Report Formula**: Viewpoint + Reasoning + Evidence + Conclusion  \n  - **Spot Call Formula**: Gratitude + Humility + Perspective\n\n### 2. Social Interaction (社会交际)\n**Core Philosophy**: Authentic connection over performance; focus on making others feel comfortable rather than showcasing personal abilities.\n\n**Key Insight**: \"Don't worry about others' opinions—90% of people don't care about you anyway.\"\n\n### 3. Cognitive Enhancement (提升认知)\n**Methodology**: Continuous learning and mental model development to expand thinking capacity and decision-making quality.\n\n### 4. Immediate Action (立即投入)\n**Anti-Procrastination Technique**: **5-Second Rule** - When facing resistance to action, count down from 5 and act immediately.\n\n## 📈 Life Journey Context\n\n### Career Progression\n- **2014**: Started at Wensi Innovation (¥60k → ¥120k)\n- **2018**: Moved to Yuxin Technology (¥140k → ¥280k)  \n- **2022**: Joined Suyin Fintech (¥450k)\n- **2025**: Current role at Ant Group (¥640k)\n\n### Key Achievements\n- **2014**: Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, Zhengzhou University\n- **2015**: Marriage to Yajing, birth of first son Hengheng\n- **2019**: Birth of second son Anan\n- **2023**: First MCN profit (¥10,200), PMP certification\n- **2024**: Learned swimming, passed Senior Information Systems Project Management exam\n- **2025**: Shanghai talent introduction residency approval\n\n### Evolution of Goals\n- **2016-2017**: Initial entrepreneurial exploration (gaming, e-commerce, mobile apps)\n- **2018**: Focus shift to professional IT career development\n- **2019**: Dual-track approach (professional growth + side income)\n- **2020-Present**: Strategic career advancement in fintech with clear progression targets\n\n## 💡 Current Life Philosophy\n\n**Core Values**: \n- **Family First**: \"The most precious thing I have is my family\"\n- **Courageous Focus**: Commit fully to chosen paths rather than scattered efforts\n- **Feynman Learning**: Use output to drive input, create strong goal-plan connections\n- **Sunk Cost Awareness**: Recognize when to cut losses and redirect energy\n\n**Current Priorities**:\n1. **Professional Excellence**: Establish expertise in fintech at Ant Group\n2. **Family Stability**: Secure housing and education for children in Taicang\n3. **Continuous Learning**: Pursue FRM certification and AI research publication\n4. **Financial Independence**: Execute disciplined investment strategy aligned with life goals\n\n## 🎯 Integration with Main Agent Responsibilities\n\nAs the personal butler and system coordinator, the Main Agent now incorporates these core principles into:\n\n- **Communication Protocol**: Apply structured expression frameworks when coordinating between agents\n- **Decision Framework**: Use What-Why-How methodology for system recommendations  \n- **Action Coordination**: Implement 5-second rule for urgent task execution\n- **Social Interface**: Maintain authentic, comfortable interaction style in user communications\n\nThis core module provides the foundational philosophy that guides all agent interactions and system decisions, ensuring alignment with the user's fundamental life principles and long-term vision."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":226470,"output":996,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":227466,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772103076311}}
