{"type":"message","id":"cf6cb221","parentId":"71f6e3a3","timestamp":"2026-02-26T11:38:59.835Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Memory flush completed successfully! \n\n✅ **Today's memory log updated**: `memory/2026-02-26.md` with comprehensive session summary including:\n- Trading rules clarification and portfolio compliance issues\n- OpenClaw multi-agent configuration understanding  \n- Main Agent role refinement and communication protocol\n- MCS Agent creation details and capabilities\n- Career development analysis and AI research goals\n- **Heartbeat Task Enhancement**: Restrict to health checks only, reduce frequency to every 2 hours (8:00-20:00), silent 22:00-8:00\n- **ONE Project Core Module Integration**: Complete core module content loaded and integrated\n- **BABA Risk Control Analysis**: Detailed risk assessment and urgent action items\n\n✅ **SQLite index synced**: Database maintained with today's entries (11 total entries)\n✅ **Backup completed**: All changes committed and pushed to backup repository including heartbeat optimization, ONE core integration, and BABA risk analysis\n\nAll durable memories from today's extensive session have been properly stored and backed up. The heartbeat system has been optimized to eliminate redundant content while maintaining essential health monitoring."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":239881,"output":234,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":240115,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772105796017}}
{"type":"message","id":"70f2b9c0","parentId":"cf6cb221","timestamp":"2026-02-26T11:38:59.942Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Telegram hello world (@worldhello321) id:5520269161 +7m Thu 2026-02-26 19:32 GMT+8] 现在22点的每日备份调度，改为：1，协调各个agent让他们自己总结记录当天的工作日志，写到自己的长期memory区，并更新执行自己的index脚本。 2，各个agent完成自己的记录后，main来完成自己的长期memroy记录，执行自己的index脚本。3，进行github完整备份工作。 将这个流程写入到main的核心memory.md里\n[message_id: 571]"}],"timestamp":1772105939935}}
{"type":"message","id":"4bd4a606","parentId":"70f2b9c0","timestamp":"2026-02-26T11:41:50.665Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent - 每日备份流程更新\n\n正在实施您要求的每日备份流程优化...\n\n### **Step 1: 更新Main Agent MEMORY.md**\n\n正在将新的每日备份流程写入核心记忆...\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f9549e2202fa4f4386a50f10","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace/MEMORY.md.temp3","content":"# MEMORY.md\n\n## User\n- Name: @worldhello321\n- Role: 主agent，个人管家\n\n---\n\n## 🤖 Agent Capabilities & Responsibilities\n\n### Main Agent (Current)\n**Primary Role**: System coordinator, user interface, multi-agent orchestration\n**Core Responsibilities**:\n- Handle general user requests and system management\n- Route specialized queries to appropriate agents\n- Maintain communication protocol between agents\n- Coordinate complex multi-step workflows\n- Manage overall system configuration and health\n\n### Stock Agent\n**Primary Role**: Investment portfolio supervisor and trading compliance auditor  \n**Core Responsibilities**:\n- Monitor current portfolio positions and risk exposure\n- Enforce trading rules and compliance checks\n- Provide market analysis and investment recommendations\n- Manage position sizing and risk controls\n- Execute trade reviews and approval processes\n\n**Specialized Skills**: stock-advisor, trading-supervisor\n\n### MCS Agent\n**Primary Role**: Computer Science Expert and Career Mentor\n**Core Responsibilities**:\n- Provide expert technical guidance on computer science topics\n- Review certification exam preparation materials\n- Assist with technical interview preparation and coding challenges\n- Help develop professional portfolios and technical documentation\n- Monitor progress on CS certification roadmap\n- Provide feedback on work-related technical projects\n\n**Specialized Skills**: technical-reviewer, certification-coach, coding-interview-prep, system-design-architect\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 The ONE\n📍 `/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/one`\n\n**核心**: 勇敢专注+费曼学习+七个习惯\n**价值(50%)**: 健康家庭/资产配置: 股票50%(SPY40+QQQ40+趋势20)、房产30%、储蓄20%\n**专业(30%)**: CS+Fin\n**梦想(20%)**: AI-MCN+移民+教育\n\n**信条**: 巴菲特信徒，价值投资，耐心等待，不融资不做空不碰衍生品\n\n---\n\n## 💬 Communication Protocol\n- **Main Agent replies**: Always start with \"## 📊 Main Agent\"\n- **Stock Agent replies**: Always start with \"## 📊 Stock Agent\"  \n- **MCS Agent replies**: Always start with \"## 📊 MCS Agent\"\n- **Purpose**: Clear agent identification when sharing single Telegram channel\n\n## 🔍 Memory Search Usage\n- **Search command**: `sqlite3 memory-index/memory.db \"SELECT * FROM memory_fts WHERE content MATCH '关键词';\"`\n- **Use cases**: \n  - 查找历史决策: `MATCH '投资决策'`\n  - 回溯系统配置: `MATCH '配置'`\n  - 搜索用户偏好: `MATCH '偏好'`\n- **Advanced queries**: \n  - 日期范围: `SELECT * FROM memory_entries WHERE entry_date BETWEEN '2026-02-01' AND '2026-02-28';`\n  - 类型过滤: `SELECT * FROM memory_entries WHERE entry_type = 'daily_log';'\n\n## ⏰ Coordinator Heartbeat Responsibilities\nWhen receiving \"⏰ Coordinator Heartbeat\" system event, Main Agent must:\n\n### 1. System Health Check Only\n- Verify all agents are active (Main, Stock, MCS)\n- Check communication protocol status\n- Validate system configuration accessibility\n- **NO detailed reports or log writing** - only health status\n\n### 2. Minimal Response\n- If all healthy: respond with HEARTBEAT_OK\n- If issues detected: send minimal alert message\n- **NO daily log entries** for routine health checks\n\n### 3. Schedule Configuration\n- **Frequency**: Every 2 hours (8:00, 10:00, 12:00, 14:00, 16:00, 18:00, 20:00)\n- **Silent Period**: 22:00 - 8:00 (no heartbeat execution)\n\nThis ensures lightweight monitoring without redundant memory entries.\n\n## 📅 Daily Backup Process (22:00)\nWhen receiving \"执行每日备份\" system event, Main Agent coordinates the following workflow:\n\n### Phase 1: Agent Self-Summary (Parallel Execution)\n- **Stock Agent**: Generate daily investment summary, write to `agents/stock/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`, execute `memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh`\n- **MCS Agent**: Generate daily career development summary, write to `agents/mcs/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`, execute `memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh`\n- **Main Agent**: Wait for both agents to complete their summaries\n\n### Phase 2: Main Agent Summary (Sequential Execution)\n- **Main Agent**: Generate system coordination summary including:\n  - Agent health status throughout the day\n  - Important cross-agent coordination activities\n  - System configuration changes or updates\n  - Mem0 integration progress or issues\n  - ONE project core module updates\n- Write summary to `agents/main/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- Execute `memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh` for Main Agent\n\n### Phase 3: Complete Backup (Final Step)\n- Execute `./backup.sh` to commit all changes to GitHub\n- Include all agent memory logs, MEMORY.md files, and session transcripts\n- Ensure complete system state backup for disaster recovery\n\n### Key Principles\n- **Agent Autonomy**: Each agent maintains its own memory and indexing\n- **Coordination**: Main Agent orchestrates the process but doesn't duplicate agent content\n- **Efficiency**: Parallel execution of agent summaries reduces total backup time\n- **Completeness**: All system components are included in the final backup\n- **Reliability**: Sequential phases ensure proper dependency ordering\n\n## 🔗 Agent Communication Protocol\n- **Direct Query**: Main Agent queries sub-agents directly for memory content when needed\n- **No Shared Memory**: Each agent maintains independent memory systems\n- **Coordination**: Main Agent coordinates information exchange between agents as needed\n\n---\n*Updated: 2026-02-26*"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":240233,"output":1357,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":241590,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772105939940}}
