control order setup\n- [ ] **Confirm**: ORCL position classification\n- [ ] **Start**: BABA phased accumulation plan (each ≤1%)\n\n### Medium-term Goals (2-8 weeks)\n- [ ] **Complete**: BABA 20% target position (10% cyclical + 10% trend)\n- [ ] **Establish**: SPY/QQQ 40% long-term core position\n- [ ] **Optimize**: Overall asset allocation to target ratios\n\n## 🔍 Market Risk Monitoring\n\n### Individual Stock Risks\n- **BABA**: Chinese ADR policy uncertainty, high volatility\n- **NVDA**: High valuation + technical resistance, increased pullback risk\n- **ORCL**: Cloud business solid but valuation not low\n\n### Overall Market\n- Increased volatility, cautious phased position building required\n- US stocks at highs, long-term position building needs technical support levels\n\n## 📝 Daily Notes\n- Continuous heartbeat checks show consistent status\n- Pending items priority unchanged from previous days\n- Ready to execute user-confirmed operations\n\n---\n*Generated by Stock Agent Daily Backup Process*"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":250343,"output":781,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":251124,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772114493319}}
